body:
Seems like with the TF 1.1.0 release there are now warnings about this deprecation but little in the way of instructions:
```
export (from tensorflow.contrib.session_bundle.exporter) is deprecated and
will be removed after 2017-06-30.
Instructions for updating:
Please use SavedModel instead.
```
